<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='336000' id='t-336000'>In fact, on Twitter,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338000' id='t-338000'>there were a number of people who were supportive of the revolution</span>
