<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='350000' id='t-350000'>But the problem is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352000' id='t-352000'>how do you decide who is in power to make these decisions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='355000' id='t-355000'>and how do you make sure</span>
