</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376000' id='t-376000'>The reality is</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='378000' id='t-378000'>that even in democratic societies today,</span>
