<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='404000' id='t-404000'>in which the United States government and some companies have handled Wikileaks.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407000' id='t-407000'>Amazon webhosting dropped Wikileaks as a customer</span>
