<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='423000' id='t-423000'>So we assume</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425000' id='t-425000'>that the Internet is a border-busting technology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='428000' id='t-428000'>This is a map of social networks worldwide,</span>
