<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='438000' id='t-438000'>the way Facebook manages its service.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440000' id='t-440000'>But borders do persist</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442000' id='t-442000'>in some parts of cyberspace.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='444000' id='t-444000'>In Brazil and Japan,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='446000' id='t-446000'>it's for unique cultural and linguistic reasons.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449000' id='t-449000'>But if you look at China, Vietnam</span>
