<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='456000' id='t-456000'>You have a situation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='458000' id='t-458000'>where the relationship between government</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='460000' id='t-460000'>and local social networking companies</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463000' id='t-463000'>is creating a situation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='465000' id='t-465000'>where, effectively,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>the empowering potential of these platforms</span>
