 8:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>Now in China,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478000' id='t-478000'>you have the &quot;great firewall,&quot; as it's well-known,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480000' id='t-480000'>that blocks Facebook</span>
