<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488000' id='t-488000'>And that's done in part with the help from Western technology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491000' id='t-491000'>But that's only half of the story.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494000' id='t-494000'>The other part of the story</span>
