<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504000' id='t-504000'>In plain English, that means censorship and surveillance</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507000' id='t-507000'>of their users.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='509000' id='t-509000'>And this is a ceremony I actually attended in 2009</span>
