</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>In Russia, they do not generally block the Internet</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535000' id='t-535000'>and directly censor websites.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='537000' id='t-537000'>But this is a website called Rospil</span>
