</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593000' id='t-593000'>So the important question, I think,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595000' id='t-595000'>is not this debate over whether the Internet</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597000' id='t-597000'>is going to help the good guys more than the bad guys.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600000' id='t-600000'>Of course, it's going to empower</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602000' id='t-602000'>whoever is most skilled at using the technology</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='605000' id='t-605000'>and best understands the Internet</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607000' id='t-607000'>in comparison with whoever their adversary is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='610000' id='t-610000'>The most urgent question we need to be asking today</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='613000' id='t-613000'>is how do we make sure</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615000' id='t-615000'>that the Internet evolves</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='617000' id='t-617000'>in a citizen-centric manner.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620000' id='t-620000'>Because I think all of you will agree</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622000' id='t-622000'>that the only legitimate purpose of government</span>
