<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686000' id='t-686000'>as being a disproportionate violation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689000' id='t-689000'>of citizens' right to communications,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='691000' id='t-691000'>and has raised questions amongst civil society groups</span>
