<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696000' id='t-696000'>some political representatives</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698000' id='t-698000'>are more interested in preserving</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700000' id='t-700000'>the interests of the entertainment industry</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703000' id='t-703000'>than they are in defending the rights of their citizens.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705000' id='t-705000'>And here in the United Kingdom</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707000' id='t-707000'>there's also concern over</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709000' id='t-709000'>a law called the Digital Economy Act</span>
